Galaxy Skipper are rotating single strain Sativa PRJs that are designed to increase a retailer's basket size. Using a handpicked selection of Canada's top craft producers Space Race Cannabis is able to continually improve its products. Galaxy Skipper are hand twisted, individually weighed and used best in-class papers for an even and smooth burn.

Product Name: Ghost Train Haze 1 x 0.5g Infused Pre-Roll
Description: Classic Station House pre-rolls made from whole flower Ghost Train Haze -- is now available in an Infused 'Express' train. A strong sativa with aromas of citrus and florals, the Infused Express Tickets is made with a proprietary blend of THCa Isolate. Precisely weighed and machine-rolled for an ideal, even burn.

Ghost Train Haze single Pre-Roll is perfect for the solo traveler. A sativa with crisp, fresh and energizing aromas of citrus and florals. This powerful sativa is distinguished by dense buds blanketed in white, crystal-capped trichomes. Ghost Train Haze comes in a convenient pop-top tube. Perfectly rolled every time for a smooth burn. Quality cannabis, everyday fares.

Welcome to Deep Space. Small, potent and ready-to-go, Deep Space Ginger Ale Galaxy is full-flavoured and bold, offering the gingery bite of a classic ginger ale but with a unique Deep Space Twist. Fueled by 10mg THC, this infused carbonated beverage comes in a 222ml sleek can.

Glueberry OG is an evenly-balanced hybrid strain characterized by bright green buds, orange pistils and frosty white trichomes. With high levels of myrcene, caryophyllene, and farnesene in its terpene profile, Glueberry OG exudes a sweet, fruity and earthy aroma. Derived from crossing OG Kush, Gorilla Glue and Blueberry strains, this triple threat lineage packs a punch with THC levels between 14-20%. Now available in perfectly packed at 0.4g per Pre-Roll and come in a 10-pack that's Redee to be enjoyed.

SHRED is back with a new way to enjoy your fav curated blends. Our Gnarberry Dartz take one of our classic aromatic blends, which is known for dreamy berry and fruity aromas, and stuffs it into 10 x 0.40g straight rolls. These smooth-burning Pre-Rolls come in a handy cardboard carrying case to prevent those Dartz from getting smooshed.

Gnarberry just got gnarlier. SHRED heavies come in a doob tube full of 3 x 0.5g pre-rolls, infused with distillate for just a bit more oomph. The fine aromatic pre-milled SHRED you know - Gnarberry, berry and fruity - now at 35-40% THC thanks to science.

Product Name: Grape Ape 1 x 1g Resin Infused Pre-Roll
Description: Multipacks are great for sharing, but what if you want one just for yourself? We heard and we acted. Introducing the Resin Infused 1x1g pre-roll. Not to big and not to small, perfect for personal consumption. Featuring the already in-demand strain Grape Ape, these single packs are great for your wallet and even better for a solo chill night.

Product Name: Grape Ape 3 x 0.5g Resin Infused Pre-Rolls
Description: DAB Bods resin-infused pre-rolls are custom designed for people who truly love cannabis and only want the most out of their experience. Starting with locally grown craft bud and delicately infusing it with our top-selling resin to provide a smooth smoke with the power kick of a concentrate. The resin-infused pre-rolls maintain all of the terpenes from the live plant and combines them with cured, hand-crafted flower in a convenient 0.5g format for individual consumption. These pre-rolls feature the popular strain 'Grape Ape' - an indica-dominant hybrid strain that has been known for its strong genetics - Afghani and Medocino Purps. Robust flavours of ripe grapes and sweet berry citrus flavour profiles explode out of these three-pack pre-rolls. Providing you a perfect combination of concentrate and pre-roll, Dab Bods infused pre-rolls are a must have to share with friends.

Product Name: Green Key Lime Hash Rosin 1 x 4.2g Soft Chew
Description: RGB's Key Lime Hash Rosin gummies feature 10mg of THC each, a super-dose of full-spectrum cannabis made without solvents. Available in a delicious 1-pack, this soft chew will transform an ordinary day into something really special. Sweet with a touch of bitter sour, these refreshing old-school style soft chews are packed with classic summertime dessert flavours. Visualize your cannabis experience and ride the spectrum. This Key Lime Hash Rosin Soft Chew is part of our Green product line - go cosmic and dive into the divine.

Dab Bods Green Monkey Moon Rocket Blunts are derived from the powerful combination of top flower, resin and kief packing 2 grams of impressively high THC levels. Convenient to consume and revealing the fully balanced strain 'GGC also known as Gods Green Crack' you will enter into another planet of happy and euphoric, energetic brain and body numbing spaces. It features flavours that bring out hints of wood, herbs and fruit with spicy, earthy aftertones. Indicative of its combined lineage God Bud and Green Crack, this has been know to be one of the most powerful and highly sought after phenos. Similar to the popular 'moonrocks' which are well known to the illicit market, this provides an easy to consume option with an extra special wrap. 1 x 2 gram blunt per pack.

Product Name: Greenhouse Variety Pack 14g (4 x 3.5g) Dried flower
Description: Sample the best of the TGOD greenhouse with the Greenhouse Variety Pack, featuring four unique 3.5gs: Organic Sugar Bush, Organic Maple Kush, Organic Cherry Mints and Organic Gold Butter MAC. All cultivars are grown in living soil at our Ancaster, ON facility, nourished by natural sunlight and purified rainwater and hang dried for max flavour and bag appeal. Each one offers very strong THC potency potential and a unique flavour profile showcasing the diverse possibilities of growing organic cannabis sustainably.

Product Name: Guava Lime Go Time Heavies 3 x 0.5g Infused Pre-Rolls
Description: Another heavyweight enters the SHRED X Heavies lineup! Prepare for an electrifying experience, and the bright & invigorating flavours of Guava Lime Go-Time. Each Diamond, Disty & terp-infused pre-roll has an exhilarating aroma profile, but that's not all... these Heavies contain THCV! The 3:1 ratio brings the headline number up to 30% THC and 10% THCV per joint. 3 x 0.5g infused pre-rolls in one handy tube. It goes without saying our SHRED X Heavies are not for lightweights!

Dab Bods Hawaiian Shatter Infused Pre Rolls are a new twist on Canada's favorite form of concentrate mixed with the most convenient form of flower. Featuring a 3 pack of 0.5 gram pre rolls combined with delicate fragments of shatter, these easy to consume joints are sure to impress. Offering full spectrum shatter already famous for being popular and potent, this sativa dominant strain is recognized for its smooth experience and happy, peaceful effects - reminiscent of a tropical party of flavours while you are relaxing on the beach. The parental genetics are a perfect combination of Pineapple Express and Amnesia Haze. Using Butane Hydrocarbon extraction techniques and some of our most popular grown flower, we bring to you a synergistic pack with some killer entourage effects seen only in full spectrum products.

Dab Bods shatter offers a high-quality hydrocarbon cannabis concentrate with impressive cannabanoid potencies up to 80 per cent, and a translucent, glass-like consistency that is easy to dab vape or add to dry flower. Ideal for those who are new to dabbing, or looking for a high-value offering that doesn't skimp on the THC, this sativa-heavy extract is priced and positioned to appeal to those who want the very best, on a budget.

Vacay Island Punch is a delicious blend of cherry and citrus flavours, with the perfect level of sweetness and carbonation for the ultimate chill refreshment. Made with SoRSE cannabis emulsion technology to deliver a predictable and consistent onset with almost no cannabis taste or smell. 10 mg of THC and 10 mg of CBD per can.

Product Name: Japanese Citrus Yuzu Wana Sour 2 x 4.5g Soft Chews
Description: Japanese Citrus Yuzu 2:1 Wana Sour Gummies combine hints of distinct acidity and unique sweetness inspired by this rare Asian fruit. Handcrafted with vegan and gluten-free ingredients, each gummie is infused with 10 mg CBD and 5 mg THC terpene-enhanced distillate creating a 2:1 ratio.

Jealousy X Apples & Bananas Pre-Rolls by Truro Cannabis are a potent legacy Indica Dominant Hybrid.  Jealousy is a 50/50 Hybrid strain produced by crossing Sherbert Bx1 with Gelato 41.  Compound Genetics and Cookies collaborated to create Apples & Bananas: a combination of a Platinum Cookies and Granddaddy Purple Hybrid with a Blue Power male. They crossed the resulting Hybrid with Gelatti to create Apples & Bananas. Flavour profile is earthy and gassy with hints of spice.  
Jealousy X Apples & Bananas Pre-Rolls are produced from the whole flower of our best-in-class batches, and we have refined our mixing and milling processes to mirror the high quality and THC levels of our popular whole flower products.  All Truro Pre-Rolls are weighed and hand-packaged in 100% recyclable tubes for a best-in-class craft pre-roll experience.
Jean Guy, no gimmicks just nugs. These namesake buds are deep green, covered in trichomes and pack a citrusy punch. Don't sleep on the Good Supply.

A fragrant bath fizz infused with full-spectrum CBD extract and soothing lavender. Dissolve in a warm bath to enjoy a full body soak. These bath bombs are hypoallergenic, free of colourants and made with lavender flowers and essential oils.

With a sweet scent and unique colour, this genetic comes from Vancouver Island, British Columbia. A classic Indica, these buds are large and dense. Whatever is not green or purple is definitely a trichome.

Product Name: Mandarin C x Tangie 1.0 g Prefilled Vape Cartridge
Description: Sweet and Sour like a Tangerine! Fresh like freshly squeezed, expect an incredibly refreshing tangerine flavour from this epic cart. The Endgame crew wanted to bring together the best citrus flavours to ignite your taste buds. This sativa dominant cart is a great choice for some fun in the sun.

Life's a little sweeter in the back forty and you won't want to wait for dessert to give our Mandarin Cookies a try! This sativa-dominant banger pulls a tangy citrus flavour with a hint of sweet nuttiness on the exhale. A cross of the classic Cookies strain and Mandarin Sunset, with some major limonene, it's all you'll need when the sun goes down.

Product Name: Mango Haze Balanced 1.0 g Prefilled Vape Cartridge
Description: Foray is an accessible entry point for anybody -- at any stage of their cannabis journey. Foray's Mango Haze is a balanced (one part THC to one part CBD) vape cartridge, and is an approachable potency for anyone on their cannabis journey. Whether you're new to vaping cannabis or well experienced, Foray's Mango Haze is sure to satsify. Mango Haze has an initial fruity, tropical flavour and subtle earthy undertone taste and aroma, with a persistent burst of orange citrus notes. This premium distillate is in a no-leak cartridge system and is calibrated to work best with Foray's 510 Thread Battery. Foray is an approachable brand that aims to both celebrate and guide one's foray into cannabis, ultimately inviting them to see cannabis differently. Device not included.

Let the mania begin...

Description: Bask in a splash of sunshine! The slightly tart and summery sweet flavour of Marionberry CBG Pearls are the perfect compliment to your perfect day with 10mg CBG per piece. Each pack has 25 Pearls for a total of 250mg of CBG!

Four elevated organic milk chocolate salted caramels nestled inside; once you try, you'll understand why it's our most-loved chocolate.

Description: A delicious medley of 30mg CBD gummies, busting with bright and balanced flavours for a perfect 'me' moment. For the discount smoker looking for something different, Potluck is a new take on the 'value ounce' -- featuring whole-flower pouches designed for mixing and matching your way to an ounce. Potluck is available in Indica, Sativa, Hybrid 7g options. The word pot-luck appears in the 16th century English work of Thomas Nashe, and used to mean 'food provided for an unexpected or uninvited guest, the luck of the pot'. Potluck dinners are events where the attendees bring a dish to a meal - a different meal. Potluck Sativa with Pineapple Express is a classic sativa strain  made by crossing Trainwreck with Hawaiian. This strain packs a punch to your palate with bright citrus notes infused with pineapple and earthy pine, thanks to the terpenes of caryophyllene, limonene and pinene.

Product Name: Pineapple Express Electric Dartz 10x0.4g Super Slim Pre-Rolls
Description: Dab Bods Electric Dartz bring to you an explosion of flavour in an easy to consume cigarette style Pre-Roll. Winner of the summer 2023 Endgame in-house selection - a guaranteed banger, flavour sensation with some of our highest THC% to date.

Made with natural flavours and colours.

Product Name: Rainbow Burst 1.2 g Prefilled Vape Cartridge
Description: BOXHOT RETRO PRESENTS: Rainbow Burst, a 1.2 g 510-threaded vape boasting up to 1000 mg of THC and some of the purest cannabis distillate available on the market. Smoke the rainbow with this tangy fruit infusion of cherry, grape, and lime. This colourful explosion of flavour will blow you away. All BOXHOT vapes are manufactured with exclusive, oversized hardware, making them optimized for big, full hits. Better yet, all BOXHOT vapes are produced with industry-leading CO2 extraction and refining processes and feature an entourage of expertly infused premium strain-specific terpenes.

Smoke the rainbow with BOXHOT Rainbow Burst Dusties. With a colourful explosion of tangy cherry, grape, and lime flavour that will blow you away, this stack of shit-kickers are infused with some dy-no-mite distillate and a tasty botanical terp blend. To top 'er off, we've coated these lil' rascals in kief to pack a potent punch that leaves other half-grammers in the dust.

You know the old saying: 'Something Gnar, something Blue, something... Peach?' Introducing SHRED X Rainbow Heavies! The best way to try out a few of our absurdly potent diamond, disty & terp-infused pre-rolls. 3 x 0.5g joints at the eye-popping 40%+ THC level. 1 x Blueberry Blaster. 1 x Mother Pucker Peach & 1 x Gnarberry. Sapphire is dried, sieved cannabis also known as 'kief', referring to the granular/powdery accumulation of trichome heads, which are the resin glands where cannabinoids and terpenes live. It's the dry sift process that separates the trichome heads from the plant, minimizing the amount of plant material in the end product. Kief has many different uses -- you can sprinkle it onto your bowl, add it to your roll, cook with it, press it into hash or heat press it into rosin. Sapphire is a powerhouse cannabis product with extremely high THC potency. Recommended for experienced cannabis consumers only.
